Title: Speed of the internationalization process: The role of diversity and depth in experiential learning
Pages: 85-101
Author-Name: Jos&eacute; C Casillas
Author-Workplace-Name: Departamento de Administraci&oacute;n de Empresas y Marketing, Universidad de Sevilla, Sevilla, Spain
Author-Name: Ana M Moreno-Men&eacute;ndez
