Title: A dynamic capabilities-based entrepreneurial theory of the multinational enterprise
Pages: 8-37
Author-Name: David J Teece
Author-Workplace-Name: Institute for Business Innovation, Haas School of Business, UC Berkeley, USA
File-URL: http://www.palgrave-journals.com/jibs/journal/v45/n1/pdf/jibs201354a.pdf
File-Format: Application/pdf
